did.unittitle: Program of Film and Media Studies records
did.abstract: Files of the Smith College Program of Film and Media Studies, including information on the program's operation, events, and student projects.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: Materials in the Smith College Archives are open for use, with the following exceptions: "Office Files," files of records created for the use of the administrative unit that created them, are closed to research for a period of 10 years following their creation.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: Transferred from the Program of Film and Media Studies, prepared by the Office of the Provost/Dean of Faculty

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: Smith College retains copyright of materials created as part of its business operations.
